>> time required: ~30 minutes
>> course: breakfast
>> serves: 8

Combine @flour{2%cups}, @sugar{2%Tbsp}, @baking powder{1%Tbsp}, and @salt{1%tsp} and set aside.

In another #bowl{}, #whisk{} together @milk{1 3/4%cups}, @vegetable oil{1/3%cup}, and @eggs{2}.

Gradually add liquid mixture to the dry mix and stir until blended.

Pour 2/3 - 3/4 cup of batter into the #waffle maker{}, close cover, and cook for ~{6-7%minutes} (golden brown)

